Lucide icons for the embedded @zenith/icons-lucide library.

Source project: Lucide
Homepage:       https://lucide.dev/
Repository:     https://github.com/lucide-icons/lucide
Tag:            1.23.0
Commit:         c67c9bdbfb43b0ecd69b52d37aeb4ab2d5386271
License:        ISC AND MIT
                (ISC for Lucide; MIT for the Feather-derived icons that the
                 upstream LICENSE enumerates. Both texts are reproduced below.)

The SVG files in this directory are the complete, byte-for-byte upstream icon set
at the revision above. Nothing is reformatted, minified, or redrawn. Re-vendoring
is therefore a plain copy of `icons/*.svg` from that tree.

Icon ids are the file stems. Search metadata (tags, categories) lives in
library.kdl, derived from the upstream `icons/<name>.json` sidecars.

Three names this project previously shipped are not upstream icon names at this
revision. They survive as search tags on their upstream equivalents, not as ids:

  sync           -> refresh-cw      (a Zenith-local rename; never an upstream name)
  upload-cloud   -> cloud-upload    (recorded upstream alias)
  download-cloud -> cloud-download  (recorded upstream alias)

